:06:00.000Z","msg":"如果未天光四五點起身衝，咁我覺得都辛苦。最多需要就一日..<br />\n<br />\n但七八點起身出門口去玩同做野，其實好正常..。好多人返工返學都係咁<br />\n<br />\n你所謂既一大早係幾點？<br />\n<br />\n我聽過有D人覺得要訓到十點甚至十二點先起身，咁樣叫一早既開始，真係幾幸福既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7470a56ab1c7c729a18493c10a8f8c92bbbc3bc3","tid":2277124,"uid":201975,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"對段關係好或者對兩者自身都好既改變無問題<br />\n覺得人既自我有好大部分<br />\n唔係改變咗某個部分就叫無咗自我既<br />\n最緊要代表到你嗰部分要堅持住<br />\n同埋係佢面前你做唔做到自己？<br />\n大家都會對方努力、磨合又未曾唔係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84f28a269993f6e367c110dd35873c2307ff94d","tid":2277124,"uid":358554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7470a56ab1c7c729a18493c10a8f8c92bbbc3bc3","tid":2277124,"uid":201975,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"對段關係好或者對兩者自身都好既改變無問題<br />\n覺得人既自我有好大部分<br />\n唔係改變咗某個部分就叫無咗自我既<br />\n最緊要代表到你嗰部分要堅持住<br />\n同埋係佢面前你做唔做到自己？<br />\n大家都會對方努力、磨合又未曾唔係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bb34b6655ba883d97ad55c4cd3161f50d519e3","tid":2277124,"uid":30251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"你後join唔得咩<br />\n或者直頭skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7d2a5e3f541dd5e7d36a81f2f8016d20a2d556","tid":2277124,"uid":348821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de422f1b16ee6082ed28e1d262159bad39bf61af","tid":2277124,"uid":358554,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"58f2270fd2f4de39db0f56be1c99d9d1707fd020","tid":2277124,"uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bbdbbb37d9a2b2b1c84128c54d6eb8b2d2d959e","tid":2277124,"uid":358554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"係咪一段關係入面拍到冇哂自我